<subSubSection id="C31F6529FF9643096AD3F089FB9ED82A" pageId="0" pageNumber="596" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="8BBA36A2FF9643096AD3F089FB9ED82A" blockId="0.[151,1436,834,1282]" pageId="0" pageNumber="596">
<emphasis id="B971EAB0FF9643096AD3F089FE83D9F6" box="[199,329,1221,1245]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="596" reason="1">
<emphasis id="B971EAB0FF9643096AD3F089FE88D9F6" bold="true" box="[199,322,1221,1245]" pageId="0" pageNumber="596">Etymology</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
The replacement generic name is a compound noun derived from the dedication to Dr Akira Hirayama of the homonym 
<taxonomicName id="4C054D21FF9643096B5AF0A6FE05D82A" authorityName="Bousfield &amp; Hoover" authorityYear="1997" box="[334,463,1258,1281]" class="Malacostraca" family="Corophiidae" genus="Hirayamaia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="0" pageNumber="596" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B971EAB0FF9643096B5AF0A6FE05D82A" box="[334,463,1258,1281]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="596">Hirayamaia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Dr. Bousfield, together with the genus name 
<taxonomicName id="4C054D21FF96430969C1F0A5FB84D82A" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1806" box="[981,1102,1257,1281]" class="Malacostraca" family="Corophiidae" genus="Corophium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="0" pageNumber="596" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B971EAB0FF96430969C1F0A5FB84D82A" box="[981,1102,1257,1281]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="596">Corophium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
